                     <interp inst="t17770910-31-off166" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a silver watch, value 40 s a steel chain, value 6 d. and two steel seals, value 4 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770910-31-victim333" type="victimName">
                     Richard
                      Minifra
                  <interp inst="t17770910-31-victim333" type="surname" value="Minifra"></interp>
